{"article_id":"YIbPZTUAtqLD8TtK","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Democratic National Committee is offering its `` deep and sincere apology '' to Bernie Sanders , his supporters and the entire party","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"for what it calls `` the inexcusable remarks","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"made over email . ''","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"Incoming interim party leader Donna Brazile and six other officials said","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"the emails `` do not reflect the values of the DNC or our steadfast commitment to neutrality during the nominating process . ''","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"It was n't signed by the outgoing DNC head , Debbie Wasserman Schultz ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"who announced Monday","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that she will not gavel in her party 's national convention .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"`` I have decided","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that in the interest","depth":12},{"id":10,"text":"of making sure","depth":13},{"id":11,"text":"that we can start the Democratic convention on a high note","depth":13},{"id":12,"text":"that I am not going to gavel in the convention , ''","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"Wasserman Schultz told the Sun Sentinel of Ft. Lauderdale ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"according to The Associated Press .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"In the wake of an email scandal , Wasserman Schultz said Sunday","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"that she will resign her post as chairwoman of the DNC after the Democratic National Convention .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Hillary Clinton 's campaign manager , Robby Mook , said","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"it was `` her decision '' to step down .","depth":4},{"id":19,"text":"Clinton is all set to accept the Democratic Party 's nomination for president .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"She will be the first woman ever","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"to rise to such a position .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"But that story is taking a backseat to the controversy","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"brewing inside the Democratic Party .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Thousands of leaked emails show a supposedly impartial DNC","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"working to secure the nomination for Clinton ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"even trying to paint the Jewish Bernie Sanders as an atheist to voters in the South .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"The scandal comes as no surprise to Sanders ' supporters","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"who see Clinton as too establishment and cozy with Wall Street .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"`` I think","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"the Clinton people stole it .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"The corruption has become more well-known with the WikiLeaks and such , ''","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"claimed one Sanders supporter .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"Meanwhile , Clinton has hired Wasserman Schultz","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"to be a part of her campaign ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"according to Townhall.com .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"The Democratic presidential candidate sent an email to supporters ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"announcing","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Wasserman Schultz would become the `` honorary chair '' of the 50-state program","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"to make sure","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"Democrats win at the polls across the country .","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"Opponents of the Florida congresswoman heckled her at a breakfast of state delegates Monday ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"shouting ,","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"`` Shame ! ''","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"and `` You 're ruining our democracy ! ''","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"Supporters of Sanders displayed paper signs","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"that said","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"`` E-mails '' on one side","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"and `` Thanks for the 'help ' Debbie , '' on the other .","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"Wasserman Schultz told the crowd during the uproar","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"that `` we have to make sure","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"that we move together in a unified way . ''","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"The Hill.com reports","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"that `` allies '' of Clinton believe","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"Wasserman Schultz should not even stay on as DNC chairwoman during the convention .","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"The news outlet says","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"one ally referred to what happened at the Florida breakfast as a reason .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"`` It 's causing the distraction","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"no one wanted at the convention , ''","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"one Clinton ally said ,","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"according to The Hill .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"Wasserman Schultz 's resignation after the convention , however , does n't mean the end of the disunity problems .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Liberals","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"unhappy with Clinton 's vice presidential pick , Sen. Tim Kaine , are looking to cause a stir .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"`` There 's talk about walking out of the vice presidential or presidential acceptance speech .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"There 's talk about total silence ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"remaining seated , turning backs , ''","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Normon Solomon , with the Bernie Delegates Network , said .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Even with this drama , the reality is Clinton will be the nominee .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"She then faces the challenge","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"of reaching out to disgruntled progressives ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"while striking a more moderate tone for the General Election .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"`` It has been the Democratic Party 's history","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"once the nominee is established","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"and we know who that 's going to be","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"and we rally the troops","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"and folks tend to come inside the tent .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"Of course , there are those","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"who are not coming in the tent","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"and they were never coming in the tent","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"and that 's okay , ''","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Leah Daughtry , CEO of the DNC , said .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"All eyes will be on Sanders","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"to see what he says to delegates Monday evening .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"Meanwhile , Kaine will be facing the biggest speech of his career .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Liberals are n't happy","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"he 's the vice presidential choice","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"and conservatives think","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"he 's too liberal ,","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"which leads many Democrats to believe","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"he 's just right .","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"The reality about Kaine is that","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"once people know him ,","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"they tend to like him","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"- even if they disagree with him .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"And he 's never lost an election .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"`` I am so excited .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"I 've known Tim Kaine for many years","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"and so I know his heart .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"I know his heart and his commitment , ''","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"reflected Alexis Herman , former secretary of labor .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"Coming off one of the biggest days of his life","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"Sen. Kaine walked through his Richmond neighborhood with his wife Anne to Saint Elizabeth Catholic Church .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"It 's","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"where","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"the couple has worshipped for three decades .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"Inside , Kaine got emotional at times","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"and even sang a solo in the choir .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"Although he has worked to reduce abortions ,","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"he 's come under fire for his support of pro-choice policies .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"`` He 's a committed Catholic , a social justice Catholic .","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"He takes that very seriously .","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"His work in politics is his outreach , ''","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"Daughtry said .","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"Several hundred Democrats followed Kaine 's example","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"by gathering in Philadelphia at an interfaith service Sunday .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"Rev . James Forbes of the Riverside Church says","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"this week Americans will see a vastly different vision for the future .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"`` I would wish","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"that the world gets a chance","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"to see two major options","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"- an option","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"that they remember from people","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"who are angry ,","depth":16},{"id":125,"text":"who are afraid --","depth":16},{"id":126,"text":"versus a group","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"that 's willing to risk possibilities","depth":16},{"id":128,"text":"that could probably do it together ,","depth":16},{"id":129,"text":"but that the prospect of our working together is even brighter , ''","depth":15},{"id":130,"text":"Forbes told News .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"So far , it 's been a mixed bag","depth":2},{"id":132,"text":"but the week is young .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":265,"left":263,"right":264,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":151,"right":262,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":149,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":147,"right":148,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{